0.7.1

Bugs fixed:
-Changing of default search provider wouldn't have immediate effect while searching
-Fixed various conditions for selecting text and hiding cursor
-Split WebView into a separate QML as well
-Removed the ScrollView since it didn't offer much benefit for now

0.7.0

Features added:
-Search engine selection
-Confirmation dialogs
-Select, Cut, Copy, Paste for address bar
-Share dialog is now working
-Possibility to edit bookmarks
-Added initial version of scrollbar

Bugs fixed:
-Address bar selection behavior is working better
-App menu will now hide when visible and tapping on it

Others:
-Major code cleanup and rework into separate file